User/Char merged, got rid of User. Ai updated to reflect that.

Refactoring stuff and putting main menu in maps as it's the same concept.

Someone didn't pull changes before they committed their changes and pushed, deleting a good bit of some one elses work, so I'm restoring the old versions so that everyone could pull as needed. Please pull and correct merge errors before pushing.
